effect.@en:
During each in-game season, you can take advantage of the following appropriate Traits:
   In spring, anytime you generate a Critical Success after rolling D100, automatically add one Fortune Point to the Fortune Pool;
   In summer, at your option you may substitute Incantation in place of any Skill required to Resist Magick spells;
   In autumn, you never suffer mental Peril as a result of failed Resolve Tests nor Corruption due to it.
   In winter, whenever you succeed at casting Magick, you do not expend reagents. This benefit does not apply to Rituals.
